1.0.name: wordpress/wp-ro-social
1.0.description: Based on Sociable WP RoSocial automatically add links to romanian social bookmarking sites on your posts or pages. You can choose from a list of 18 websites/tools. [Ro] Bazat pe Sociable, WP RoSocial adaugat automat linkuri spre cele mai cunoscute site-uri de tipul social bookmarking romanesti in fiecare post sau pagina de pe blogul tau (in functie de setari).
